question: What is the highest mountain in Australia?

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {
	?uri rdf:type dbo:Mountain .
        ?uri dbo:locatedInArea res:Australia .
        ?uri dbo:elevation ?elevation .
} 
ORDER BY DESC(?elevation) LIMIT 1

question: For which label did Elvis record his first album?

PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {
        ?x rdf:type dbo:Album .
        ?x dbo:artist res:Elvis_Presley .
        ?x dbo:releaseDate ?y .
        ?x dbo:recordLabel ?uri .

ORDER BY ASC(?y)

question: Give me all cities in New Jersey with more than 100000 inhabitants.
keywords: New Jersey, city, inhabitants, more than 100000
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {
	?uri rdf:type dbo:City .
        ?uri dbo:isPartOf res:New_Jersey .
        ?uri dbp:populationTotal ?inhabitants .
        FILTER (?inhabitants > 100000) .
}
